<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>TimeBlock - 15 Minute Time Tracker</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <main>
        <header>
            <h1>TimeBlock</h1>
            <p>A simple tool to track your day in 15-minute blocks.</p>
        </header>

        <section>
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <p>
                TimeBlock helps you see where your time goes. Each day is split
                into 15-minute slots that you can label with what you were working on.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Track your day in 15-minute blocks</li>
                <li>Add a block by entering a time, activity, and project</li>
                <li>Delete blocks you don't need</li>
                <li>Blocks are saved so they persist between sessions</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
